{
  "materi": "pertidaksamaan-linear",
  "sections": [
    {
      "id": "B",
      "title": "Pertidaksamaan Linear Satu Variabel",
      "contoh": [
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 1",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Nyatakan pertidaksamaan untuk setiap garis bilangan berikut.<br><br><strong>(a)</strong> Lingkaran penuh di $x = 2$, garis ke kanan.<br><strong>(b)</strong> Lingkaran terbuka di $x = 5$, garis ke kiri.<br><strong>(c)</strong> Lingkaran terbuka di $x = -2$, lingkaran penuh di $x = 4$, ruas di antara keduanya.</p>",
          "p": "<br><strong>(a)</strong> Lingkaran <strong>penuh</strong> di $x = 2$, garis ke kanan $\\Rightarrow \\boldsymbol{x \\geq 2}$<br><div class=\"nline-wrap\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 220 45\" width=\"220\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><marker id=\"b1a\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#3B82F6\"/></marker><marker id=\"b1b\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#888\"/></marker></defs><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"210\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#b1b)\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"10\" y2=\"24\"/><line x1=\"60\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"60\" y2=\"24\"/><line x1=\"110\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"110\" y2=\"24\"/><line x1=\"160\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"160\" y2=\"24\"/><text x=\"10\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">0</text><text x=\"60\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">1</text><text x=\"110\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">2</text><text x=\"160\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">3</text><circle cx=\"110\" cy=\"22\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"#3B82F6\"/><line x1=\"110\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"205\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#3B82F6\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" marker-end=\"url(#b1a)\"/></svg></div><br><strong>(b)</strong> Lingkaran <strong>terbuka</strong> di $x = 5$, garis ke kiri $\\Rightarrow \\boldsymbol{x &lt; 5}$<br><div class=\"nline-wrap\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 260 45\" width=\"260\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><marker id=\"b2a\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"1\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M6,0 L6,6 L0,3z\" fill=\"#e53e3e\"/></marker><marker id=\"b2b\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#888\"/></marker></defs><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"250\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#b2b)\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"10\" y2=\"24\"/><line x1=\"60\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"60\" y2=\"24\"/><line x1=\"110\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"110\" y2=\"24\"/><line x1=\"160\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"160\" y2=\"24\"/><line x1=\"210\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"210\" y2=\"24\"/><text x=\"10\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">2</text><text x=\"60\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">3</text><text x=\"110\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">4</text><text x=\"160\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">5</text><text x=\"210\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">6</text><circle cx=\"160\" cy=\"22\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"white\" stroke=\"#e53e3e\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><line x1=\"15\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"155\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#e53e3e\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" marker-start=\"url(#b2a)\"/></svg></div><br><strong>(c)</strong> Lingkaran terbuka di $x = -2$, lingkaran penuh di $x = 4$ $\\Rightarrow \\boldsymbol{-2 &lt; x \\leq 4}$<br><div class=\"nline-wrap\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 340 45\" width=\"340\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><marker id=\"b3b\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#888\"/></marker></defs><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"330\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#b3b)\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"10\" y2=\"24\"/><line x1=\"60\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"60\" y2=\"24\"/><line x1=\"110\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"110\" y2=\"24\"/><line x1=\"160\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"160\" y2=\"24\"/><line x1=\"210\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"210\" y2=\"24\"/><line x1=\"260\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"260\" y2=\"24\"/><line x1=\"310\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"310\" y2=\"24\"/><text x=\"10\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">-4</text><text x=\"60\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">-3</text><text x=\"110\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">-2</text><text x=\"160\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">-1</text><text x=\"210\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">0</text><text x=\"260\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">2</text><text x=\"310\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">4</text><circle cx=\"110\" cy=\"22\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"white\" stroke=\"#8B5CF6\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><circle cx=\"310\" cy=\"22\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"#8B5CF6\"/><line x1=\"115\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"310\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#8B5CF6\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"/></svg></div>"
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 2",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Tentukan interval penyelesaian $3x - 6 &lt; 12$.</p>",
          "p": "<br> $$\\begin{align*} 3x - 6 &< 12 \\\\ 3x &< 18 \\\\ x &< 6 \\end{align*}$$ Interval penyelesaian: $x &lt; 6$ <div class=\"nline-wrap\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 220 45\" width=\"220\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><marker id=\"c2a\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"1\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M6,0 L6,6 L0,3z\" fill=\"#e53e3e\"/></marker><marker id=\"c2b\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#888\"/></marker></defs><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"210\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#c2b)\"/><text x=\"20\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">3</text><text x=\"70\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">4</text><text x=\"120\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">5</text><text x=\"170\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">6</text><circle cx=\"170\" cy=\"22\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"white\" stroke=\"#e53e3e\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><line x1=\"15\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"165\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#e53e3e\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" marker-start=\"url(#c2a)\"/></svg></div>"
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 3",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Tentukan interval penyelesaian $5x + 3 \\geq 3x - 7$.</p>",
          "p": "<br> $$\\begin{align*} 5x + 3 &\\geq 3x - 7 \\\\ 5x - 3x &\\geq -7 - 3 \\\\ 2x &\\geq -10 \\\\ x &\\geq -5 \\end{align*}$$ Interval penyelesaian: $x \\geq -5$ <div class=\"nline-wrap\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 200 45\" width=\"200\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><marker id=\"c3a\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#3B82F6\"/></marker><marker id=\"c3b\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#888\"/></marker></defs><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"190\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#c3b)\"/><text x=\"40\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">-7</text><text x=\"80\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">-6</text><text x=\"120\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">-5</text><text x=\"160\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">-4</text><circle cx=\"120\" cy=\"22\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"#3B82F6\"/><line x1=\"120\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"185\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#3B82F6\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" marker-end=\"url(#c3a)\"/></svg></div>"
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 4",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Tentukan interval penyelesaian $3x - 5 \\geq 7x + 11$.</p>",
          "p": "<br> $$\\begin{align*} 3x - 5 &\\geq 7x + 11 \\\\ 3x - 7x &\\geq 11 + 5 \\\\ -4x &\\geq 16 \\\\ x &\\leq -4 \\quad \\text{(tanda berbalik karena dibagi } -4\\text{)} \\end{align*}$$ Interval penyelesaian: $x \\leq -4$ <div class=\"nline-wrap\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 200 45\" width=\"200\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><marker id=\"c4a\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"1\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M6,0 L6,6 L0,3z\" fill=\"#3B82F6\"/></marker><marker id=\"c4b\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#888\"/></marker></defs><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"190\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#c4b)\"/><text x=\"30\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">-7</text><text x=\"80\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">-5</text><text x=\"130\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">-4</text><text x=\"170\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">-2</text><circle cx=\"130\" cy=\"22\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"#3B82F6\"/><line x1=\"15\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"130\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#3B82F6\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" marker-start=\"url(#c4a)\"/></svg></div>"
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 5",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Tentukan interval penyelesaian $4x - 6 &lt; 9x - 21$.</p>",
          "p": "<br> $$\\begin{align*} 4x - 6 &< 9x - 21 \\\\ 4x - 9x &< -21 + 6 \\\\ -5x &< -15 \\\\ x &> 3 \\quad \\text{(tanda berbalik karena dibagi } -5\\text{)} \\end{align*}$$ Interval penyelesaian: $x > 3$ <div class=\"nline-wrap\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 180 45\" width=\"180\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><marker id=\"c5a\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#e53e3e\"/></marker><marker id=\"c5b\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#888\"/></marker></defs><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"170\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#c5b)\"/><text x=\"30\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">1</text><text x=\"70\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">2</text><text x=\"110\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">3</text><text x=\"150\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">4</text><circle cx=\"110\" cy=\"22\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"white\" stroke=\"#e53e3e\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><line x1=\"115\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"165\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#e53e3e\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" marker-end=\"url(#c5a)\"/></svg></div>"
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 6",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Tentukan interval penyelesaian $-8 &lt; 3x + 4 &lt; 22$.</p>",
          "p": "<br> $$\\begin{align*} -8 &< 3x + 4 < 22 \\\\ -8-4 &< 3x < 22-4 \\\\ -12 &< 3x < 18 \\\\ -4 &< x < 6 \\end{align*}$$ Interval penyelesaian: $-4 &lt; x &lt; 6$ <div class=\"nline-wrap\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 220 45\" width=\"220\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><marker id=\"c6b\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#888\"/></marker></defs><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"210\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#c6b)\"/><text x=\"30\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">-6</text><text x=\"80\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">-4</text><text x=\"150\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">6</text><circle cx=\"80\" cy=\"22\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"white\" stroke=\"#8B5CF6\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><circle cx=\"150\" cy=\"22\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"white\" stroke=\"#8B5CF6\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><line x1=\"85\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"145\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#8B5CF6\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"/></svg></div>"
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 7",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Tentukan interval penyelesaian $-3 \\leq 9 - 4x \\leq 29$.</p>",
          "p": "<br> $$\\begin{align*} -3 &\\leq 9-4x \\leq 29 \\\\ -3-9 &\\leq -4x \\leq 29-9 \\\\ -12 &\\leq -4x \\leq 20 \\\\ 3 &\\geq x \\geq -5 \\quad \\text{(tanda berbalik karena dibagi } -4\\text{)} \\\\ -5 &\\leq x \\leq 3 \\end{align*}$$ Interval penyelesaian: $-5 \\leq x \\leq 3$ <div class=\"nline-wrap\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 220 45\" width=\"220\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><marker id=\"c7b\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#888\"/></marker></defs><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"210\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#c7b)\"/><text x=\"40\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">-6</text><text x=\"80\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">-5</text><text x=\"150\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">3</text><text x=\"190\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">5</text><circle cx=\"80\" cy=\"22\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"#059669\"/><circle cx=\"150\" cy=\"22\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"#059669\"/><line x1=\"80\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"150\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#059669\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"/></svg></div>"
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 8",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Tentukan interval penyelesaian $5 - 2x \\leq 4x - 7 &lt; x + 8$.</p>",
          "p": "<br> Karena semua bagian memuat variabel, pecah menjadi dua pertidaksamaan:<br><br><strong>Bagian kiri:</strong> $$\\begin{align*} 5-2x &\\leq 4x-7 \\\\ -6x &\\leq -12 \\\\ x &\\geq 2 \\quad \\cdots(1) \\end{align*}$$ <strong>Bagian kanan:</strong> $$\\begin{align*} 4x-7 &< x+8 \\\\ 3x &< 15 \\\\ x &< 5 \\quad \\cdots(2) \\end{align*}$$ Gabungkan (1) dan (2): $\\boldsymbol{2 \\leq x &lt; 5}$ <div class=\"nline-wrap\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 200 45\" width=\"200\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><marker id=\"c8b\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#888\"/></marker></defs><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"190\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#c8b)\"/><text x=\"40\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">1</text><text x=\"90\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">2</text><text x=\"140\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">5</text><circle cx=\"90\" cy=\"22\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"#059669\"/><circle cx=\"140\" cy=\"22\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"white\" stroke=\"#059669\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><line x1=\"90\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"140\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#059669\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"/></svg></div>"
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 9",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Tentukan interval penyelesaian $4 + 2x &lt; 3x - 2 \\leq x + 6$.</p>",
          "p": "<br><strong>Bagian kiri:</strong> $$\\begin{align*} 4+2x &< 3x-2 \\\\ -x &< -6 \\\\ x &> 6 \\quad \\cdots(1) \\end{align*}$$ <strong>Bagian kanan:</strong> $$\\begin{align*} 3x-2 &\\leq x+6 \\\\ 2x &\\leq 8 \\\\ x &\\leq 4 \\quad \\cdots(2) \\end{align*}$$ Dari (1) dan (2): syarat $x > 6$ dan $x \\leq 4$ tidak dapat dipenuhi sekaligus. $$\\boxed{HP = \\emptyset \\text{ (tidak ada nilai } x \\text{ yang memenuhi)}}$$"
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 10",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Tentukan interval penyelesaian $\\dfrac{2x+1}{3} - \\dfrac{x-2}{4} > 1$.</p>",
          "p": "<br> KPK dari penyebut $3$ dan $4$ adalah $12$. Kalikan semua suku dengan $12$: $$\\begin{align*} 4(2x+1) - 3(x-2) &> 12 \\\\ 8x+4-3x+6 &> 12 \\\\ 5x+10 &> 12 \\\\ 5x &> 2 \\\\ x &> \\frac{2}{5} \\end{align*}$$ Interval penyelesaian: $x > \\dfrac{2}{5}$ <div class=\"nline-wrap\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 180 45\" width=\"180\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><marker id=\"c10a\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#e53e3e\"/></marker><marker id=\"c10b\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#888\"/></marker></defs><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"170\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#c10b)\"/><text x=\"40\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">-1</text><text x=\"90\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">2/5</text><text x=\"140\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">1</text><circle cx=\"90\" cy=\"22\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"white\" stroke=\"#e53e3e\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><line x1=\"95\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"165\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#e53e3e\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" marker-end=\"url(#c10a)\"/></svg></div>"
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 11",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Tentukan interval penyelesaian $\\dfrac{3x-1}{2} \\leq \\dfrac{x+3}{3} + 2$.</p>",
          "p": "<br> KPK dari penyebut $2$ dan $3$ adalah $6$. Kalikan semua suku dengan $6$: $$\\begin{align*} 3(3x-1) &\\leq 2(x+3)+12 \\\\ 9x-3 &\\leq 2x+6+12 \\\\ 7x &\\leq 21 \\\\ x &\\leq 3 \\end{align*}$$ Interval penyelesaian: $x \\leq 3$"
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 12",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Tentukan interval penyelesaian $\\dfrac{3(x-2)}{4} - \\dfrac{2(x+1)}{3} \\geq \\dfrac{x-5}{6}$.</p>",
          "p": "<br> KPK dari $4$, $3$, dan $6$ adalah $12$. Kalikan semua suku dengan $12$: $$\\begin{align*} 3 \\cdot 3(x-2) - 4 \\cdot 2(x+1) &\\geq 2(x-5) \\\\ 9(x-2)-8(x+1) &\\geq 2x-10 \\\\ 9x-18-8x-8 &\\geq 2x-10 \\\\ x-26 &\\geq 2x-10 \\\\ -x &\\geq 16 \\\\ x &\\leq -16 \\end{align*}$$ Interval penyelesaian: $x \\leq -16$"
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 13",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Tentukan nilai $x$ bulat yang memenuhi kedua pertidaksamaan berikut secara bersamaan: $$2(x-3) &lt; x + 1 \\quad \\text{dan} \\quad 3(x+2) \\geq 2x + 10$$</p>",
          "p": "<br><strong>Pertidaksamaan 1:</strong> $$\\begin{align*} 2x-6 &< x+1 \\\\ x &< 7 \\quad \\cdots(1) \\end{align*}$$ <strong>Pertidaksamaan 2:</strong> $$\\begin{align*} 3x+6 &\\geq 2x+10 \\\\ x &\\geq 4 \\quad \\cdots(2) \\end{align*}$$ Irisan (1) dan (2): $4 \\leq x &lt; 7$<br> Nilai $x$ bulat yang memenuhi: $\\boldsymbol{x \\in \\{4, 5, 6\\}}$. <div class=\"nline-wrap\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 200 45\" width=\"200\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><marker id=\"c13b\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#888\"/></marker></defs><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"190\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#c13b)\"/><text x=\"30\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">3</text><text x=\"80\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">4</text><text x=\"150\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">7</text><text x=\"180\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">8</text><circle cx=\"80\" cy=\"22\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"#059669\"/><circle cx=\"150\" cy=\"22\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"white\" stroke=\"#059669\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><line x1=\"80\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"145\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#059669\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"/></svg></div>"
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 14",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Sederhanakan setiap kondisi berikut:<br><strong>(a)</strong> $x > 3$ dan $x \\leq 6$ &ensp; <strong>(b)</strong> $x \\geq 4$ dan $x > 7$ &ensp; <strong>(c)</strong> $x &lt; 4$ atau $x \\leq 9$</p>",
          "p": "<br><strong>(a)</strong> Irisan: ambil yang lebih ketat dari kiri dan kanan $\\Rightarrow$ $\\boldsymbol{3 &lt; x \\leq 6}$<br><br><strong>(b)</strong> Irisan dua kondisi arah sama: $x \\geq 4$ dan $x > 7$ $\\Rightarrow$ ambil $\\max(4,7)$ $\\Rightarrow$ $\\boldsymbol{x > 7}$<br><br><strong>(c)</strong> Gabungan: ambil yang lebih lebar $\\Rightarrow$ $x \\leq 9$ mencakup $x &lt; 4$ $\\Rightarrow$ $\\boldsymbol{x \\leq 9}$"
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 15",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Tentukan nilai $x$ yang memenuhi:<br><strong>(a)</strong> $x > 7$ dan $x &lt; 3$ &ensp; <strong>(b)</strong> $x > 5$ atau $x &lt; 9$</p>",
          "p": "<br><strong>(a)</strong> Syarat $x > 7$ dan $x &lt; 3$: tidak ada bilangan yang sekaligus lebih dari 7 dan kurang dari 3.<br> $\\Rightarrow$ $\\boldsymbol{HP = \\emptyset}$ (himpunan kosong).<br><br><strong>(b)</strong> Syarat $x > 5$ atau $x &lt; 9$: karena $5 &lt; 9$, setiap bilangan real pasti memenuhi setidaknya satu kondisi.<br> $\\Rightarrow$ $\\boldsymbol{HP = \\mathbb{R}}$ (semua bilangan real)."
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 16",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Andi ingin membeli beberapa buku tulis seharga Rp5.000 per buah. Ia memiliki uang sebesar Rp40.000 dan ingin menyisakan minimal Rp7.500 untuk ongkos pulang. Berapa buku tulis maksimal yang dapat dibeli Andi?</p>",
          "p": "<br> Misalkan banyak buku yang dibeli adalah $n$ buah. Syarat uang tersisa minimal Rp7.500: $$\\begin{align*} 40.000 - 5.000n &\\geq 7.500 \\\\ -5.000n &\\geq -32.500 \\\\ n &\\leq 6{,}5 \\end{align*}$$ Karena $n$ harus bilangan bulat positif, maka $n \\leq 6$. Jadi, Andi dapat membeli maksimal <strong>6 buku tulis</strong>."
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 17",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Nilai ulangan Budi untuk tiga mata pelajaran adalah 72, 78, dan 80. Berapa nilai minimal yang harus Budi peroleh pada ulangan keempat agar rata-rata nilainya tidak kurang dari 80?</p>",
          "p": "<br> Misalkan nilai ulangan keempat adalah $x$. Syarat rata-rata $\\geq 80$: $$\\begin{align*} \\frac{72+78+80+x}{4} &\\geq 80 \\\\ \\frac{230+x}{4} &\\geq 80 \\\\ 230+x &\\geq 320 \\\\ x &\\geq 90 \\end{align*}$$ Jadi, Budi harus mendapatkan nilai minimal <strong>90</strong> pada ulangan keempat."
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 18",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Suatu pabrik menghasilkan dua jenis produk A dan B. Setiap produk A memerlukan 3 jam mesin dan setiap produk B memerlukan 5 jam mesin. Total waktu mesin tersedia 120 jam per minggu. Jika pabrik harus menghasilkan setidaknya 10 unit A dan setidaknya 8 unit B, tentukan rentang banyaknya produk A yang dapat diproduksi!</p>",
          "p": "<br> Misalkan banyaknya produk A adalah $a$ dan produk B adalah $b$. Kendala: $$3a + 5b \\leq 120, \\quad a \\geq 10, \\quad b \\geq 8$$ Substitusi $b = 8$ (nilai minimum B) untuk memperoleh batas atas A: $$\\begin{align*} 3a + 5(8) &\\leq 120 \\\\ 3a &\\leq 80 \\\\ a &\\leq 26{,}67 \\end{align*}$$ Karena $a$ bilangan bulat, maka $a \\leq 26$. Sehingga: $\\boldsymbol{10 \\leq a \\leq 26}$. <div class=\"nline-wrap\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 220 45\" width=\"220\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><marker id=\"c18b\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#888\"/></marker></defs><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"210\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#c18b)\"/><text x=\"30\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">8</text><text x=\"80\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">10</text><text x=\"170\" y=\"37\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">26</text><circle cx=\"80\" cy=\"22\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"#059669\"/><circle cx=\"170\" cy=\"22\" r=\"4.5\" fill=\"#059669\"/><line x1=\"80\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"170\" y2=\"22\" stroke=\"#059669\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"/></svg></div>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "C",
      "title": "Pertidaksamaan Linear Dua Variabel",
      "contoh": [
        {
          "section": "C",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 19",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Gambarlah daerah penyelesaian dari $2x + 3y \\leq 12$.</p>",
          "p": "<br><strong>Langkah 1.</strong> Garis batas: $2x + 3y = 12$. Titik potong sumbu $x$: $(6, 0)$. Titik potong sumbu $y$: $(0, 4)$.<br><br><strong>Langkah 2.</strong> Tanda $\\leq$ $\\Rightarrow$ garis digambar <strong>penuh</strong>.<br><br><strong>Langkah 3.</strong> Uji titik $(0, 0)$: $2(0)+3(0) = 0 \\leq 12$ ✓. Daerah HP memuat $(0,0)$. <div class=\"grafik-wrap\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 240 200\" width=\"240\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><marker id=\"d19x\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#555\"/></marker><marker id=\"d19y\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#555\"/></marker></defs><g stroke=\"#e2e8f0\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"><line x1=\"30\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"30\" y2=\"185\"/><line x1=\"70\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"70\" y2=\"185\"/><line x1=\"110\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"110\" y2=\"185\"/><line x1=\"150\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"150\" y2=\"185\"/><line x1=\"190\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"190\" y2=\"185\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"45\" x2=\"225\" y2=\"45\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"85\" x2=\"225\" y2=\"85\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"125\" x2=\"225\" y2=\"125\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"165\" x2=\"225\" y2=\"165\"/></g><polygon points=\"30,165 190,165 30,45\" fill=\"#3B82F6\" fill-opacity=\"0.18\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"165\" x2=\"225\" y2=\"165\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#d19x)\"/><line x1=\"30\" y1=\"185\" x2=\"30\" y2=\"10\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#d19y)\"/><line x1=\"190\" y1=\"165\" x2=\"30\" y2=\"45\" stroke=\"#3B82F6\" stroke-width=\"2.2\"/><circle cx=\"190\" cy=\"165\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#333\"/><circle cx=\"30\" cy=\"45\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#333\"/><circle cx=\"30\" cy=\"165\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#555\"/><text x=\"190\" y=\"178\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">(6,0)</text><text x=\"45\" y=\"40\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\">(0,4)</text><text x=\"22\" y=\"177\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\">O</text><text x=\"80\" y=\"140\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#3B82F6\" font-weight=\"bold\">HP</text><text x=\"120\" y=\"90\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#3B82F6\" transform=\"rotate(-34,120,90)\">2x+3y=12</text><text x=\"70\" y=\"175\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\" text-anchor=\"middle\">2</text><text x=\"110\" y=\"175\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\" text-anchor=\"middle\">4</text><text x=\"150\" y=\"175\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\" text-anchor=\"middle\">5</text><text x=\"22\" y=\"128\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\">1</text><text x=\"22\" y=\"88\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\">2</text><text x=\"22\" y=\"48\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\">4</text></svg></div>"
        },
        {
          "section": "C",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 20",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Gambarlah daerah penyelesaian dari $x - 2y > 4$.</p>",
          "p": "<br><strong>Langkah 1.</strong> Garis batas: $x - 2y = 4$. Titik potong sumbu $x$: $(4, 0)$. Titik potong sumbu $y$: $(0, -2)$.<br><br><strong>Langkah 2.</strong> Tanda $>$ $\\Rightarrow$ garis digambar <strong>putus-putus</strong>.<br><br><strong>Langkah 3.</strong> Uji titik $(0, 0)$: $0 - 0 = 0 > 4$? <strong>Salah.</strong> Daerah HP adalah bagian yang <em>tidak</em> memuat $(0,0)$. <div class=\"grafik-wrap\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 260 200\" width=\"260\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><marker id=\"d20x\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#555\"/></marker><marker id=\"d20y\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#555\"/></marker></defs><g stroke=\"#e2e8f0\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"><line x1=\"30\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"30\" y2=\"195\"/><line x1=\"65\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"65\" y2=\"195\"/><line x1=\"100\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"100\" y2=\"195\"/><line x1=\"135\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"135\" y2=\"195\"/><line x1=\"170\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"170\" y2=\"195\"/><line x1=\"205\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"205\" y2=\"195\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"30\" x2=\"250\" y2=\"30\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"65\" x2=\"250\" y2=\"65\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"100\" x2=\"250\" y2=\"100\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"135\" x2=\"250\" y2=\"135\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"170\" x2=\"250\" y2=\"170\"/></g><polygon points=\"135,100 245,100 245,10 30,10 30,135\" fill=\"#e53e3e\" fill-opacity=\"0.14\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"100\" x2=\"250\" y2=\"100\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#d20x)\"/><line x1=\"30\" y1=\"195\" x2=\"30\" y2=\"10\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#d20y)\"/><line x1=\"135\" y1=\"100\" x2=\"30\" y2=\"135\" stroke=\"#e53e3e\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" stroke-dasharray=\"6,4\"/><line x1=\"135\" y1=\"100\" x2=\"245\" y2=\"65\" stroke=\"#e53e3e\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" stroke-dasharray=\"6,4\"/><circle cx=\"135\" cy=\"100\" r=\"5\" fill=\"white\" stroke=\"#e53e3e\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><circle cx=\"30\" cy=\"135\" r=\"5\" fill=\"white\" stroke=\"#e53e3e\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><circle cx=\"30\" cy=\"100\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#555\"/><text x=\"135\" y=\"113\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">(4,0)</text><text x=\"44\" y=\"131\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\">(0,−2)</text><text x=\"22\" y=\"110\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\">O</text><text x=\"195\" y=\"82\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#e53e3e\" font-weight=\"bold\">HP</text><text x=\"170\" y=\"75\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#e53e3e\" transform=\"rotate(17,170,75)\">x−2y=4</text><text x=\"65\" y=\"109\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\" text-anchor=\"middle\">1</text><text x=\"100\" y=\"109\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\" text-anchor=\"middle\">2</text><text x=\"170\" y=\"109\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\" text-anchor=\"middle\">5</text><text x=\"22\" y=\"68\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\">2</text><text x=\"22\" y=\"33\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\">4</text><text x=\"22\" y=\"138\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\">−1</text><text x=\"22\" y=\"173\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\">−2</text></svg></div>"
        },
        {
          "section": "C",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 21",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Gambarlah daerah penyelesaian dari $3x + y \\geq 6$.</p>",
          "p": "<br><strong>Langkah 1.</strong> Garis batas: $3x + y = 6$. Titik potong sumbu $x$: $(2, 0)$. Titik potong sumbu $y$: $(0, 6)$.<br><br><strong>Langkah 2.</strong> Tanda $\\geq$ $\\Rightarrow$ garis digambar <strong>penuh</strong>.<br><br><strong>Langkah 3.</strong> Uji titik $(0, 0)$: $3(0)+0 = 0 \\geq 6$? <strong>Salah.</strong> Daerah HP adalah bagian yang <em>tidak</em> memuat $(0,0)$ — yaitu di atas/kanan garis. <div class=\"grafik-wrap\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 220 240\" width=\"220\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><marker id=\"d21x\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#555\"/></marker><marker id=\"d21y\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#555\"/></marker></defs><g stroke=\"#e2e8f0\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"><line x1=\"30\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"30\" y2=\"230\"/><line x1=\"70\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"70\" y2=\"230\"/><line x1=\"110\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"110\" y2=\"230\"/><line x1=\"150\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"150\" y2=\"230\"/><line x1=\"190\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"190\" y2=\"230\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"30\" x2=\"215\" y2=\"30\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"70\" x2=\"215\" y2=\"70\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"215\" y2=\"110\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"150\" x2=\"215\" y2=\"150\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"190\" x2=\"215\" y2=\"190\"/></g><polygon points=\"30,30 210,30 210,150 110,150\" fill=\"#059669\" fill-opacity=\"0.15\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"190\" x2=\"215\" y2=\"190\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#d21x)\"/><line x1=\"30\" y1=\"230\" x2=\"30\" y2=\"10\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#d21y)\"/><line x1=\"30\" y1=\"30\" x2=\"110\" y2=\"190\" stroke=\"#059669\" stroke-width=\"2.2\"/><circle cx=\"110\" cy=\"190\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#059669\"/><circle cx=\"30\" cy=\"30\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#059669\"/><circle cx=\"30\" cy=\"190\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#555\"/><text x=\"110\" y=\"205\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">(2,0)</text><text x=\"44\" y=\"28\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\">(0,6)</text><text x=\"22\" y=\"200\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\">O</text><text x=\"160\" y=\"100\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#059669\" font-weight=\"bold\">HP</text><text x=\"55\" y=\"110\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#059669\" transform=\"rotate(-72,55,110)\">3x+y=6</text><text x=\"70\" y=\"199\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\" text-anchor=\"middle\">1</text><text x=\"110\" y=\"199\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\" text-anchor=\"middle\">2</text><text x=\"22\" y=\"153\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\">1</text><text x=\"22\" y=\"113\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\">3</text><text x=\"22\" y=\"73\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\">5</text><text x=\"22\" y=\"33\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\">6</text></svg></div>"
        },
        {
          "section": "C",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 22",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Gambarlah daerah penyelesaian dari $y &lt; 3x$.</p>",
          "p": "<br><strong>Langkah 1.</strong> Garis batas: $y = 3x$. Garis ini melewati titik asal $(0,0)$ serta titik $(1, 3)$.<br><br><strong>Langkah 2.</strong> Tanda $&lt;$ $\\Rightarrow$ garis digambar <strong>putus-putus</strong>.<br><br><strong>Langkah 3.</strong> Karena garis melewati $(0,0)$, titik uji diganti dengan $(1, 0)$: $0 &lt; 3(1) = 3$? <strong>Benar.</strong> Daerah HP memuat $(1, 0)$ — yaitu di bawah/kanan garis. <div class=\"grafik-wrap\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 200 190\" width=\"200\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><marker id=\"d22x\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#555\"/></marker><marker id=\"d22y\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#555\"/></marker></defs><g stroke=\"#e2e8f0\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"><line x1=\"30\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"30\" y2=\"180\"/><line x1=\"70\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"70\" y2=\"180\"/><line x1=\"110\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"110\" y2=\"180\"/><line x1=\"150\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"150\" y2=\"180\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"30\" x2=\"190\" y2=\"30\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"70\" x2=\"190\" y2=\"70\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"190\" y2=\"110\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"150\" x2=\"190\" y2=\"150\"/></g><polygon points=\"30,150 70,150 190,10 190,150\" fill=\"#e53e3e\" fill-opacity=\"0.14\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"150\" x2=\"190\" y2=\"150\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#d22x)\"/><line x1=\"30\" y1=\"180\" x2=\"30\" y2=\"10\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#d22y)\"/><line x1=\"30\" y1=\"150\" x2=\"70\" y2=\"30\" stroke=\"#e53e3e\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" stroke-dasharray=\"6,4\"/><line x1=\"70\" y1=\"30\" x2=\"185\" y2=\"10\" stroke=\"#e53e3e\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" stroke-dasharray=\"6,4\"/><circle cx=\"30\" cy=\"150\" r=\"5\" fill=\"white\" stroke=\"#e53e3e\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"30\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#e53e3e\"/><text x=\"30\" y=\"165\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">O</text><text x=\"78\" y=\"28\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\">(1,3)</text><text x=\"150\" y=\"125\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#e53e3e\" font-weight=\"bold\">HP</text><text x=\"130\" y=\"25\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#e53e3e\">y=3x</text><text x=\"70\" y=\"159\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\" text-anchor=\"middle\">1</text><text x=\"110\" y=\"159\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\" text-anchor=\"middle\">2</text><text x=\"22\" y=\"113\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\">1</text><text x=\"22\" y=\"73\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\">2</text><text x=\"22\" y=\"33\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\">3</text></svg></div>"
        },
        {
          "section": "C",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 23",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Tentukan pertidaksamaan dari daerah berarsir berikut.<br><br><strong>(a)</strong> Garis <em>penuh</em> melalui $(4,0)$ dan $(0,4)$; HP memuat titik asal.<br><strong>(b)</strong> Garis <em>putus-putus</em> melalui $(3,0)$ dan $(0,6)$; HP <em>tidak</em> memuat titik asal.</p>",
          "p": "<br><strong>(a)</strong><br> 1. Garis <strong>penuh</strong> $\\Rightarrow$ tanda $\\leq$ atau $\\geq$.<br> 2. Garis melewati $(4,0)$ dan $(0,4)$: persamaan $\\dfrac{x}{4}+\\dfrac{y}{4}=1 \\Rightarrow x+y=4$.<br> 3. Uji $(0,0)$: $0+0=0 \\leq 4$ ✓ $\\Rightarrow$ tanda $\\leq$. $$\\boxed{x + y \\leq 4}$$ <strong>(b)</strong><br> 1. Garis <strong>putus-putus</strong> $\\Rightarrow$ tanda $&lt;$ atau $>$.<br> 2. Garis melewati $(3,0)$ dan $(0,6)$: persamaan $\\dfrac{x}{3}+\\dfrac{y}{6}=1 \\Rightarrow 2x+y=6$.<br> 3. Uji $(0,0)$: $0+0=0 > 6$? <strong>Salah</strong> $\\Rightarrow$ tanda harus $>$. $$\\boxed{2x + y > 6}$$"
        },
        {
          "section": "C",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 24",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Gambarlah daerah penyelesaian dari sistem pertidaksamaan: $$\\begin{cases} x + y \\leq 6 \\\\ 2x + y \\leq 8 \\\\ x \\geq 0, \\quad y \\geq 0 \\end{cases}$$</p>",
          "p": "<br><strong>Garis 1:</strong> $x+y=6$ $\\Rightarrow$ titik $(6,0)$ dan $(0,6)$.<br><strong>Garis 2:</strong> $2x+y=8$ $\\Rightarrow$ titik $(4,0)$ dan $(0,8)$.<br><br><strong>Titik potong Garis 1 dan Garis 2:</strong> $$(2x+y)-(x+y)=8-6 \\Rightarrow x=2; \\quad 2+y=6 \\Rightarrow y=4. \\quad \\text{Titik: }(2,4).$$ <strong>Uji titik $(0,0)$:</strong> $0 \\leq 6$ ✓ dan $0 \\leq 8$ ✓. HP memuat $(0,0)$.<br><br><strong>Titik-titik sudut:</strong> $O(0,0)$, $A(4,0)$, $B(2,4)$, $C(0,6)$. <div class=\"grafik-wrap\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 280 260\" width=\"280\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><marker id=\"d24x\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#555\"/></marker><marker id=\"d24y\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3z\" fill=\"#555\"/></marker></defs><g stroke=\"#e2e8f0\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"><line x1=\"30\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"30\" y2=\"250\"/><line x1=\"65\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"65\" y2=\"250\"/><line x1=\"100\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"100\" y2=\"250\"/><line x1=\"135\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"135\" y2=\"250\"/><line x1=\"170\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"170\" y2=\"250\"/><line x1=\"205\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"205\" y2=\"250\"/><line x1=\"240\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"240\" y2=\"250\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"25\" x2=\"265\" y2=\"25\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"60\" x2=\"265\" y2=\"60\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"95\" x2=\"265\" y2=\"95\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"130\" x2=\"265\" y2=\"130\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"165\" x2=\"265\" y2=\"165\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"200\" x2=\"265\" y2=\"200\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"235\" x2=\"265\" y2=\"235\"/></g><polygon points=\"30,235 135,235 100,130 30,60\" fill=\"#3B82F6\" fill-opacity=\"0.18\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"235\" x2=\"265\" y2=\"235\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#d24x)\"/><line x1=\"30\" y1=\"250\" x2=\"30\" y2=\"10\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#d24y)\"/><!-- Garis 1: x+y=6 dari (0,6)=(30,60) ke (6,0)=(240,235) --><line x1=\"30\" y1=\"60\" x2=\"240\" y2=\"235\" stroke=\"#3B82F6\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><!-- Garis 2: 2x+y=8 dari (0,8)=(30,25+8/8*210)≈ hmm let me fix scale scale: 0→30px, each unit=35px. so y=0 is at 235, y=6 is at 235-210=25. x=0 is at 30, x=6 is at 30+210=240 Garis 1: (6,0)→(240,235) (0,6)→(30,25) Garis 2: 2x+y=8. (4,0)→(30+4*35,235)=(170,235). (0,8)→(30,235-8*35)=(30,235-280)=(30,-45)—off screen. So from (170,235) to (30,25+(8-6)*35)=(30,95) is wrong, let's just show to boundary. Better approach: 2x+y=8: at y=0, x=4→(170,235); at x=0, y=8→(30,235-8*35)=(30,235-280)=(30,-45) off screen. Draw from (170,235) upward to edge. At x=0: y=8 → off screen. At y=235 (y_px), y=0, x=4. Line from (170,235) going direction: as x decreases by 1, y increases by 2, so dy/dx in px = -2*35/35=-2 per pixel. The line exits the top at some point. At top of visible area (y_px=10), y = (235-10)/35 = 6.43, then 2x=8-6.43=1.57, x=0.786 → x_px=30+0.786*35=57. So draw from (57,10) to (170,235). --><line x1=\"57\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"170\" y2=\"235\" stroke=\"#e53e3e\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><circle cx=\"30\" cy=\"235\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#555\"/><circle cx=\"170\" cy=\"235\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#555\"/><circle cx=\"30\" cy=\"60\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#555\"/><circle cx=\"240\" cy=\"235\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#888\"/><circle cx=\"100\" cy=\"130\" r=\"5\" fill=\"#333\"/><text x=\"30\" y=\"248\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">O</text><text x=\"170\" y=\"248\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">(4,0)</text><text x=\"44\" y=\"56\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\">(0,6)</text><text x=\"240\" y=\"248\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">(6,0)</text><text x=\"110\" y=\"127\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#333\">(2,4)</text><text x=\"75\" y=\"175\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#3B82F6\" font-weight=\"bold\">HP</text><text x=\"180\" y=\"145\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#3B82F6\">x+y=6</text><text x=\"80\" y=\"90\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#e53e3e\">2x+y=8</text><text x=\"65\" y=\"244\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\">1</text><text x=\"100\" y=\"244\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\">2</text><text x=\"135\" y=\"244\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\">3</text><text x=\"22\" y=\"200\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\">1</text><text x=\"22\" y=\"165\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\">2</text><text x=\"22\" y=\"130\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\">3</text><text x=\"22\" y=\"95\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\">4</text><text x=\"22\" y=\"60\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#777\">6</text></svg></div>"
        },
        {
          "section": "C",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 25",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Tentukan daerah penyelesaian dari sistem: $$\\begin{cases} 3x + 2y \\leq 24 \\\\ x + 2y \\leq 16 \\\\ x \\geq 2, \\quad y \\geq 0 \\end{cases}$$ dan tentukan titik-titik sudut daerah penyelesaian tersebut.</p>",
          "p": "<br><strong>Garis 1:</strong> $3x+2y=24$: titik $(8,0)$ dan $(0,12)$.<br><strong>Garis 2:</strong> $x+2y=16$: titik $(16,0)$ dan $(0,8)$.<br><strong>Garis 3:</strong> $x=2$ (garis vertikal).<br><br><strong>Titik potong Garis 1 dan Garis 2:</strong> $$(3x+2y)-(x+2y)=24-16 \\Rightarrow 2x=8 \\Rightarrow x=4; \\quad 4+2y=16 \\Rightarrow y=6. \\quad \\text{Titik: }(4,6).$$ <strong>Titik potong Garis 2 dengan $x=2$:</strong> $2+2y=16 \\Rightarrow y=7 \\Rightarrow$ titik $(2,7)$.<br><strong>Cek $(2,7)$ terhadap Garis 1:</strong> $3(2)+2(7)=20 \\leq 24$ ✓<br><strong>Titik potong Garis 1 dengan $x=2$:</strong> $6+2y=24 \\Rightarrow y=9 \\Rightarrow$ titik $(2,9)$.<br><strong>Cek $(2,9)$ terhadap Garis 2:</strong> $2+2(9)=20 > 16$ — <strong>tidak memenuhi</strong>; bukan titik sudut HP.<br><br><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><thead><tr><th>Titik Sudut</th><th>Keterangan</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>$(2, 0)$</td><td>Perpotongan $x=2$ dengan sumbu $x$</td></tr><tr><td>$(8, 0)$</td><td>Perpotongan Garis 1 dengan sumbu $x$</td></tr><tr><td>$(4, 6)$</td><td>Perpotongan Garis 1 dan Garis 2</td></tr><tr><td>$(2, 7)$</td><td>Perpotongan Garis 2 dengan $x=2$</td></tr></tbody></table></div>"
        },
        {
          "section": "C",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 26",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Gambarlah daerah penyelesaian dan tentukan titik-titik sudut dari sistem: $$\\begin{cases} x + 2y \\leq 8 \\\\ x - y \\leq 2 \\\\ x \\geq 0, \\quad y \\geq 0 \\end{cases}$$</p>",
          "p": "<br><strong>Garis 1:</strong> $x+2y=8$ $\\Rightarrow$ titik $(8,0)$ dan $(0,4)$.<br><strong>Garis 2:</strong> $x-y=2$ $\\Rightarrow$ titik $(2,0)$ dan $(0,-2)$.<br><br><strong>Titik potong Garis 1 dan Garis 2:</strong> $$(x+2y)-(x-y)=8-2 \\Rightarrow 3y=6 \\Rightarrow y=2; \\quad x-2=2 \\Rightarrow x=4. \\quad \\text{Titik: }(4,2).$$ <strong>Uji titik $(0,0)$:</strong> $0 \\leq 8$ ✓ dan $0 \\leq 2$ ✓. HP memuat $(0,0)$. <div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><thead><tr><th>Titik Sudut</th><th>Keterangan</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>$(0, 0)$</td><td>Titik asal</td></tr><tr><td>$(2, 0)$</td><td>Perpotongan Garis 2 dengan sumbu $x$</td></tr><tr><td>$(4, 2)$</td><td>Perpotongan Garis 1 dan Garis 2</td></tr><tr><td>$(0, 4)$</td><td>Perpotongan Garis 1 dengan sumbu $y$</td></tr></tbody></table></div>"
        },
        {
          "section": "C",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 27",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Seorang pengrajin membuat dua jenis kerajinan: tas dan dompet. Pembuatan satu tas membutuhkan 4 jam dan satu dompet membutuhkan 2 jam. Setiap hari ia hanya bisa bekerja maksimal 16 jam. Ia juga ingin membuat minimal 2 tas dan minimal 3 dompet per hari.<br><br><strong>(a)</strong> Buatlah model pertidaksamaannya jika $x$ = banyak tas dan $y$ = banyak dompet.<br><strong>(b)</strong> Gambarlah daerah penyelesaiannya.</p>",
          "p": "<br><strong>(a) Model pertidaksamaan:</strong><ul><li>Kendala waktu: $4x + 2y \\leq 16 \\;\\Rightarrow\\; 2x + y \\leq 8$</li><li>Minimal tas: $x \\geq 2$</li><li>Minimal dompet: $y \\geq 3$</li></ul> $$\\begin{cases} 2x + y \\leq 8 \\\\ x \\geq 2 \\\\ y \\geq 3 \\end{cases}$$ <strong>(b) Titik-titik sudut:</strong><br> Perpotongan $2x+y=8$ dengan $x=2$: $4+y=8 \\Rightarrow y=4$. Titik: $(2,4)$.<br> Perpotongan $2x+y=8$ dengan $y=3$: $2x+3=8 \\Rightarrow x=2{,}5$. Titik: $(2{,}5;\\,3)$.<br> Perpotongan $x=2$ dengan $y=3$: Titik $(2,3)$.<br><br> Daerah penyelesaian adalah segitiga dengan titik sudut $(2,3)$, $(2{,}5;\\,3)$, dan $(2,4)$."
        },
        {
          "section": "C",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 28",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Seorang peternak ingin memelihara ayam dan kambing. Setiap ayam membutuhkan 2 m² kandang dan setiap kambing membutuhkan 5 m² kandang. Luas kandang yang tersedia maksimal 40 m². Biaya perawatan ayam Rp10.000/bulan dan kambing Rp30.000/bulan dengan anggaran maksimal Rp180.000/bulan. Ia ingin memelihara minimal 3 ayam dan minimal 1 kambing.<br><br><strong>(a)</strong> Buatlah model pertidaksamaannya jika $x$ = jumlah ayam dan $y$ = jumlah kambing.<br><strong>(b)</strong> Gambarlah daerah penyelesaiannya dan tentukan titik-titik sudutnya.</p>",
          "p": "<br><strong>(a) Model pertidaksamaan:</strong><ul><li>Kendala kandang: $2x + 5y \\leq 40$</li><li>Kendala biaya: $10.000x + 30.000y \\leq 180.000 \\;\\Rightarrow\\; x + 3y \\leq 18$</li><li>Minimal ayam: $x \\geq 3$</li><li>Minimal kambing: $y \\geq 1$</li></ul><strong>(b) Mencari titik-titik sudut:</strong><br> Titik potong $2x+5y=40$ dan $x+3y=18$: dari persamaan kedua $x=18-3y$, substitusi: $$2(18-3y)+5y=40 \\Rightarrow 36-6y+5y=40 \\Rightarrow -y=4 \\Rightarrow y=-4.$$ Karena $y \\geq 1$, titik potong kedua garis ini di luar daerah fisibel. Perlu diperiksa titik-titik sudut dari perpotongan batas yang relevan:<br><br><ul><li>$x=3$ dan $y=1$: titik $(3,1)$. Cek: $2(3)+5(1)=11 \\leq 40$ ✓; $3+3=6 \\leq 18$ ✓.</li><li>$x+3y=18$ dan $x=3$: $3+3y=18 \\Rightarrow y=5$. Titik $(3,5)$. Cek: $2(3)+5(5)=31 \\leq 40$ ✓.</li><li>$x+3y=18$ dan $y=1$: $x+3=18 \\Rightarrow x=15$. Titik $(15,1)$. Cek: $2(15)+5(1)=35 \\leq 40$ ✓.</li><li>$2x+5y=40$ dan $y=1$: $x=17{,}5$ → Cek biaya: $17{,}5+3=20{,}5 > 18$ — tidak memenuhi kendala biaya.</li></ul><strong>Titik-titik sudut HP:</strong> $(3,1)$, $(15,1)$, $(3,5)$."
        }
      ]
    }
